---
// A static, hand-drawn-feel mockup of the Praxnote note editor for the home hero.
// SVG/HTML only, no images.
---
<div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="hv-card">
    <header class="hv-header">
      <div class="hv-avatar">JK</div>
      <div>
        <div class="hv-name">Client J.K. · Session 12</div>
        <div class="hv-meta">Referral · psychiatric eval</div>
      </div>
      <span class="hv-badge">Draft</span>
    </header>

    <nav class="hv-tabs" aria-label="Document type">
      <span>Session note</span>
      <span>Treatment plan</span>
      <span class="hv-tab-active">Referral letter</span>
      <span>Diagnosis</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="hv-context">
      <span>Intake</span>
      <span>PHQ-9 · 17</span>
      <span>Tx plan</span>
      <span>Last 3 sessions</span>
    </div>

    <div class="hv-body">
      <p>
        <strong>Reason for referral.</strong> Moderate-to-severe depressive symptoms persist despite twelve sessions of CBT. Sleep disturbance and anhedonia have not remitted; PHQ-9 trended <em>17 → 17 → 19</em> across the last six weeks.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>What I'm asking.</strong> Medication evaluation to support continued therapeutic work. Client is open to SSRI consultation; family history is significant for…
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="hv-input">
      <span class="hv-input-label">Your turn</span>
      <span class="hv-input-text">Add specifics, urgency, what you'd like back, anything the chart can't say.</span>
    </div>

    <footer class="hv-footer">
      <span class="hv-pill">PHI never sent to AI</span>
      <span class="hv-action">Edit · Sign</span>
    </footer>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-left: auto;
  }
  .hv-card {
    background: var(--surface-card);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-modal);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--stone-700);
    transform: rotate(0.3deg);
  }
  .hv-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }
  .hv-avatar {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--brand-teal-soft);
    color: var(--brand-teal-dark);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  .hv-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--stone-900); font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .hv-meta { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--stone-500); }
  .hv-badge {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    background: var(--terracotta-soft);
    color: var(--terracotta);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }
  .hv-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hv-tabs span {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    color: var(--stone-500);
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .hv-tab-active {
    background: var(--brand-teal) !important;
    color: var(--paper) !important;
    border-color: var(--brand-teal) !important;
  }
  .hv-context {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }
  .hv-context span {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    background: var(--paper-warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    color: var(--stone-700);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .hv-body {
    background: var(--paper-warm);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 0.95rem 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }
  .hv-body p { margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .hv-body p:last-child { margin: 0; }
  .hv-body em { color: var(--brand-teal-dark); font-style: italic; }

  .hv-input {
    border: 1px dashed var(--hairline-strong);
    background: rgba(243, 227, 216, 0.4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 0.7rem 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .hv-input-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--terracotta);
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }
  .hv-input-text {
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--stone-500);
  }
  .hv-footer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 0.85rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }
  .hv-pill {
    background: var(--brand-teal-soft);
    color: var(--brand-teal-dark);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
  }
  .hv-action { color: var(--brand-teal-dark); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
